	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Does it really matter what you call it? Most of us in this forum program engines at the same that we generate game content, so it really isn't possible to draw a line.
<br />
<br />Also, an unfinished game isn't much of a game. IMO, it only becomes an actual game when you finish it and it's playable from start to finish.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

