	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The engine is the code and the data that you can recycle into a new project, with which you can make another game.
<br />
<br />A game is just how you use the engine. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
